{"_path":"/maps/_web/security/supply-chain","_dir":"security","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"软件供应链安全","description":"开源软件生态中的传递性信任问题与供应链攻击防范","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"传递性信任问题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"传递性信任问题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"开源生态建立在维护者之间的传递性信任之上：一个 800 个传递依赖的包之所以能工作，\n是因为链上每个维护者都合理选择和维护了自己的依赖。\n但现有工具（npm audit、Dependabot）只能扫描已知漏洞，无法验证维护者的安全实践。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你信任你的维护者，你的维护者信任他们的维护者，但他们是否信任他们维护者的维护者？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"供应链攻击案例"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"供应链攻击案例"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"event-stream 事件"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：原维护者将项目交给新人，后者添加恶意依赖"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"xz backdoor"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：共同维护者潜伏两年后在构建系统中植入混淆代码"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"codecov bash uploader"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：CI 工具被攻击，数千项目受影响"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"信任边界的局限"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"信任边界的局限"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Trusted Publishing 和 vendoring 都只是移动了信任边界，而非消除信任需求。\n大公司的受控构建仍然依赖编译器、操作系统和硬件——\n在某处你总会停止验证，开始信任。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://nesbitt.io/2026/03/02/transitive-trust.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Transitive Trust | Andrew Nesbitt"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":